synopsis: "OCaml binding of R2Pipe"
description: """
r2pipe-ocaml is an OCaml binding of R2Pipe which used to 
automate radare2. 
It has simple internal. It just spawn a r2 with quiet mode
and then interact through In/Out channel."""
